{"word":"ἀποκαλύπτω","slug":"ἀποκαλύπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποκαλύπτω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to uncover</i>, <el>τὴν κεφαλήν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to disclose, reveal</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to reveal one's whole mind</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be disclosed, made known</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}